.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Controller</h2>\n<h2 id=\"view와-model을-이어주는-역할을-담당합니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#view%EC%99%80-model%EC%9D%84-%EC%9D%B4%EC%96%B4%EC%A3%BC%EB%8A%94-%EC%97%AD%ED%95%A0%EC%9D%84-%EB%8B%B4%EB%8B%B9%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"view와 model을 이어주는 역할을 담당합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>View와 Model을 이어주는 역할을 담당합니다.</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>이벤트를 발생시키고, Model에 전달해 View에 화면을 띄웁니다.</li>\n<li>주로 Activity, Fragment를 의미하며 MVC 패턴에서 코드가 집약됩니다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Android] MVC 패턴","date":"July 01, 2000"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Android/mvc/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Android/mvvm/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Android] MVVM 패턴"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}